<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #ffd72c;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Mentor Application Update</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{mentorName}},</p>

            {{#if approved}}
                <p>Congratulations! ðŸŽ‰ Your application to become a mentor on Flux has been approved.</p>
                <p>You can now:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Access your mentor dashboard</li>
                    <li>Set up your availability</li>
                    <li>Start accepting mentorship sessions</li>
                    <li>Connect with students</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Get started by logging into your account and completing your mentor profile.</p>
                <center>
                    <a href="https://getflux.tech" class="button">Flux Webiste</a>
                </center>
            {{else}}
                <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming a mentor on Flux.</p>
                <p>After careful review of your application, we regret to inform you that we cannot approve your application at this time.</p>
                <p>This decision was based on various factors including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Current platform requirements</li>
                    <li>Expertise alignment</li>
                    <li>Platform capacity</li>
                </ul>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for being part of the Flux community!</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 